个工作日。\"' is not assignable to type '\"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you submit your complete profile.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":52216,"length":239,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'a1' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32132,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"如果我的资料未被批准怎么办？\"' is not assignable to type '\"What happens if my profile is not approved?\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":52463,"length":49,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'q2' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32160,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"如果您的资料不符合我们的要求，我们将提供具体的反馈说明需要更新的内容。您可以进行必要的更改并重新提交。如果最终无法批准，我们在 30 天内提供全额退款。\"' is not assignable to type '\"If your profile doesn't meet our requirements, we'll provide specific feedback on what needs to be updated. You can make the necessary changes and resubmit. If approval is ultimately not possible, we offer a full refund within 30 days.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":52520,"length":241,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'a2' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32250,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"我可以升级或降级我的计划吗？\"' is not assignable to type '\"Can I upgrade or downgrade my plan?\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":52769,"length":41,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'q3' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32278,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"是的，您可以随时更改您的计划。升级时，您将被收取按比例分配的差额。降级时，新费率将在您的下一个计费周期生效。\"' is not assignable to type '\"Yes, you can change your plan at any time. When upgrading, you'll be charged the prorated difference. When downgrading, the new rate applies at your next billing cycle.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":52818,"length":174,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'a3' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32346,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"什么是创始制造商计划？\"' is not assignable to type '\"What is the Founding Manufacturer program?\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":53000,"length":48,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'q4' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32371,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"创始制造商计划是对加入 SourceNest 的前 300 家制造商的限时优惠。作为创始成员，您可以免费获得 6 个月的 Growth 计划全部功能（价值 $299/月）- 包括最多 100 个产品、高级分析、优先搜索可见性、精选供应商徽章和多个团队用户。无需信用卡即可开始。\"' is not assignable to type '\"The Founding Manufacturer program is a limited offer for the first 300 manufacturers who join SourceNest. As a founding member, you get 6 months of free access to our full Growth plan ($299/month value) - including up to 100 products, advanced analytics, priority visibility, featured supplier badge, and multiple te...'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":53056,"length":365,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'a4' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Pricing FAQ\"; readonly q1: \"Does payment automatically publish my profile?\"; readonly a1: \"No. Payment creates your manufacturer account, but your profile must still go through our review and approval process before it becomes visible to buyers. This typically takes 2-5 business days after you sub...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":32523,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"6 个月免费期结束后会发生什么？\"' is not assignable to type '\"What happens after my 6-month free period ends?\"'.","relatedInforma