"length":27,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'title' which is declared here on type '{ readonly badge: \"Trust & Quality\"; readonly title: \"Our Review Process\"; readonly description: \"Suppliers on SourceNest go through a review process based on submitted information. This process is intended to improve transparency and does not constitute verification or guarantee of any kind.\"; }'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":33601,"length":11,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"SourceNest 上的供应商要经过基于提交信息的审查流程。此流程旨在改进透明度，不构成任何形式的验证或保证。\"' is not assignable to type '\"Suppliers on SourceNest go through a review process based on submitted information. This process is intended to improve transparency and does not constitute verification or guarantee of any kind.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":55377,"length":210,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'description' which is declared here on type '{ readonly badge: \"Trust & Quality\"; readonly title: \"Our Review Process\"; readonly description: \"Suppliers on SourceNest go through a review process based on submitted information. This process is intended to improve transparency and does not constitute verification or guarantee of any kind.\"; }'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":33704,"length":5,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"为什么我们的审核流程很重要\"' is not assignable to type '\"Why Our Review Process Matters\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":55619,"length":39,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'title' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Why Our Review Process Matters\"; readonly intro: \"In the world of B2B sourcing, trust is essential. Buyers need confidence when connecting with suppliers. Traditional platforms often allow anyone to list, which can make it harder to evaluate options and requires more effort from buyers.\"; ... 5 mo...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":33734,"length":5,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"在 B2B 采购领域，信任是必不可少的。买家在与供应商建立联系时需要有信心。传统平台通常允许任何人列出商品，这可能使评估选项变得更困难，并需要买家付出更多努力。\"' is not assignable to type '\"In the world of B2B sourcing, trust is essential. Buyers need confidence when connecting with suppliers. Traditional platforms often allow anyone to list, which can make it harder to evaluate options and requires more effort from buyers.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":55666,"length":246,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'intro' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Why Our Review Process Matters\"; readonly intro: \"In the world of B2B sourcing, trust is essential. Buyers need confidence when connecting with suppliers. Traditional platforms often allow anyone to list, which can make it harder to evaluate options and requires more effort from buyers.\"; ... 5 mo...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":33831,"length":8,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"SourceNest 采取了不同的方法。我们旨在审核制造商资料和提交的信息，以帮助提高透明度，并在供应商出现在平台上之前支持做出更好的决策。\"' is not assignable to type '\"SourceNest takes a different approach. We aim to review manufacturer profiles and submitted information to help improve transparency and support better decision-making before suppliers appear on the platform.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":55920,"length":220,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'approach' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Why Our Review Process Matters\"; readonly intro: \"In the world of B2B sourcing, trust is essential. Buyers need confidence when connecting with suppliers. Traditional platforms often allow anyone to list, which can make it harder to evaluate options and requires more effort from buyers.\"; ... 5 mo...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":33921,"length":8,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"我们的流程的好处\"' is not assignable 