,"relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":71426,"length":122,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'subtitle' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Making Global Sourcing Work Better\"; readonly subtitle: \"SourceNest is on a mission to transform how businesses find and connect with manufacturing partners worldwide.\"; }'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":42660,"length":5,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"我们的故事\"' is not assignable to type '\"Our Story\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":71575,"length":18,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'title' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Our Story\"; readonly p1: \"Global sourcing has always been challenging. Buyers struggle to find reliable suppliers, review their legitimacy, and communicate effectively across borders. Manufacturers, especially quality-focused ones, have difficulty standing out among countless options and reaching ...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":42682,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"全球采购一直充满挑战。买方难以找到可靠的供应商、审查其合法性并有效跨境沟通。尤其是质量导向的制造商，很难在众多选择中脱颖而出并接触到认真的买方。\"' is not assignable to type '\"Global sourcing has always been challenging. Buyers struggle to find reliable suppliers, review their legitimacy, and communicate effectively across borders. Manufacturers, especially quality-focused ones, have difficulty standing out among countless options and reaching serious buyers.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":71601,"length":293,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'p1' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Our Story\"; readonly p1: \"Global sourcing has always been challenging. Buyers struggle to find reliable suppliers, review their legitimacy, and communicate effectively across borders. Manufacturers, especially quality-focused ones, have difficulty standing out among countless options and reaching ...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":42768,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"SourceNest 源于一个简单的想法：如果有一个平台只展示经过审核和批准的制造商呢？一个买方可以确信每个供应商在上市前都经过信息审查的地方？\"' is not assignable to type '\"SourceNest was born from a simple idea: what if there was a platform that only featured reviewed, approved manufacturers? A place where buyers could know that every supplier had been screened based on submitted information before being listed?\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":71902,"length":249,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'p2' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Our Story\"; readonly p1: \"Global sourcing has always been challenging. Buyers struggle to find reliable suppliers, review their legitimacy, and communicate effectively across borders. Manufacturers, especially quality-focused ones, have difficulty standing out among countless options and reaching ...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":42854,"length":2,"code":2322,"category":1,"messageText":"Type '\"我们建立了 SourceNest 来实现这一目标。通过要求对每个制造商进行管理员批准并为买方免费提供平台，我们创造了一个质量优先、信任成为每次联系基础的环境。\"' is not assignable to type '\"We built SourceNest to be that platform. By requiring admin approval for every manufacturer and keeping the platform free for buyers, we've created an environment where quality prevails and trust is the foundation of every connection.\"'.","relatedInformation":[{"file":"./lib/i18n/locales/en.ts","start":72159,"length":240,"messageText":"The expected type comes from property 'p3' which is declared here on type '{ readonly title: \"Our Story\"; readonly p1: \"Global sourcing has always been challenging. Buyers struggle to find reliable suppliers, review their legitimacy, and communicate effectively across borders. Manufacturers, especially quality-focused ones, have difficulty standing out among countless options and reaching ...'","category":3,"code":6500}]},{"start":42947,"length":2,"